{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-10841/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-10841"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:08:41"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man yells at a woman sitting across from him."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-10841","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-10841"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1/9b056a36-b854-4112-a337-a965f580b613","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:10:52.532Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma challenges Reynolds by suggesting that he’s not as “tough” as he acts. She, in other words, sees through his facade of cold distance, acknowledges like no one else that he’s childlike, and can read what he truly desires: a cycle of domination and care that she’ll provide with her mushroom poisonings.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:650.0675675675676,176.45903716216216,209.87964527027032,380.96072635135124"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1/641423ab-991a-4b01-8f36-ee7ca724a6ac","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T19:11:17.415Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds latches onto the word “time.” For both of them, this concept is crucial. He wants time to devote to his art; she wants time to spend with him. Symbolically, though, it’s the substance that represents what they devote themselves to.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10841/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:893.7858952702703,179.03716216216216,204.85008445945925,382.71537162162156"}}}]}]}]}